## Section 1: DEFINITIONS

**"Benefits Navigation"** means the process of helping individuals understand, compare, select, and enroll in health insurance, government assistance programs, and related benefits.

**"Competing Product"** means any product, service, or offering that provides substantially similar functionality to the Software, including AI-powered benefits navigation, health plan comparison, or government assistance guidance capabilities.

**"Derivative Work"** means any modification, adaptation, enhancement, translation, or work that is based upon or incorporates the Software or any portion thereof.

**"Noncommercial Purpose"** means personal research, experimentation, education, hobby projects, or use by a charitable organization, educational institution, public research organization, public safety or health organization, or government institution, in each case without any commercial application or financial gain.

**"Licensee" or "You"** means the individual or legal entity exercising rights under this License.

**"Licensor"** means Kealu Inc. and its authorized contributors.

**"Output"** means any content, recommendations, comparisons, or artifacts generated through use of the Software.

**"Use"** means any operation of the Software, including execution, integration, deployment, hosting, or provision as a service.

